title: Leidos Schedules Third Quarter Calendar Year 2015 Earnings Conference Call for October 29, 2015 at 8AM ET
text:
RESTON, Va. , Oct. 12, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Leidos Holdings, Inc. (Leidos) (NYSE: LDOS), a national security, health and engineering solutions company, has scheduled a conference call for Thursday, October 29, 2015 , at 8:00 AM ET to announce its third quarter calendar year 2015 financial results for the period ending Friday, October 2 , 2015. The company plans to issue its quarterly earnings press release before the conference call on October 29, 2015 .
Date: October 29, 2015
Time: 8:00 AM (ET)
To Listen via the Internet:
We are pleased to offer a live and replay audio broadcast of the conference call with corresponding slides at http://ir.leidos.com .
To Listen via Telephone:
877-377-7103 (toll-free U.S.)
+1-408-940-3826 (for International Callers)
Passcode: 51905146
Replay:
A telephone playback of the third quarter calendar year 2015 earnings conference call is scheduled to be available beginning at 11:00 AM (ET) on October 29, 2015 , through 11:59 PM (ET) on November 3 , 2015. The replay will be accessible by calling 855-859-2056 (International callers: 404-537-3406), and entering passcode 51905146.
An archived version of the webcast will be available on the Leidos Investor Relations website at http://ir.leidos.com .
About Leidos
Leidos is a science and technology solutions leader working to address some of the world's toughest challenges in national security, health and engineering. The Company's 19,000 employees support vital missions for government and the commercial sector, develop innovative solutions to drive better outcomes and defend our Nation's digital and physical infrastructure from 'new world' threats. Headquartered in Reston, Virginia , Leidos reported annual revenues of approximately $5.06 billion for its fiscal year ended January 30, 2015 . For more information, visit www.Leidos.com .
